---
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-brand-dark">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Copy -->
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block text-academy-teal text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Why Academy Daycare</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">
          We Can Take Virtually <span class="text-academy-teal">Any Dog</span> and Help Them Thrive
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Most daycares turn away difficult dogs. We specialize in them. Our team of canine behaviour experts doesn't just watch your dog — they actively work with them, building confidence, social skills, and structure.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Your Dog Only Plays With Safe, Compatible Dogs</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every dog is assessed in person by our trainers before joining. No random dogs, no unknown temperaments. Your dog is matched with companions that bring out the best in them.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Your Dog Gets Expert Attention — Not Just Supervision</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Our staff are trained canine behaviour specialists who read body language, manage group dynamics, and actively work with your dog — not part-timers scrolling their phone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Drop Off Without Worrying — 15 Years, Zero Incidents</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">15 years of socializing dogs of every breed and temperament with a flawless safety record. You go to work knowing your dog is in the safest hands in the GTA.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-1">Your Nervous Dog Builds Real Confidence — Not More Anxiety</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We match nervous dogs with calm, compatible playmates and recommend 3–5 days per week initially. Consistent exposure in a safe environment builds lasting confidence — not the overstimulation other daycares create.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-black/50">
          <img
            src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/640b7e539788904338695107/53455a7e-00c4-4747-8fee-3d156436075f/2.png"
            alt="Happy dog at Academy Daycare"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Floating stat -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 sm:bottom-6 sm:right-6 bg-brand-charcoal border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-3xl font-black text-academy-teal">15</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Years, Perfect Record</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
